Package: nimix
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Mixture Clustering and Regression with NIMBLE
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Achmad Syahrul", "Choir", email = "madsyair@stis.ac.id",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7088-0646"))
Description: Bayesian finite and nonparametric mixture models for clustering and
    regression, built on the 'nimble' package (de Valpine et al. 2017
    <doi:10.1080/10618600.2016.1172487>). Provides univariate and multivariate
    mixture components with a Dirichlet process (Chinese restaurant process)
    engine and a fixed-number-of-components engine, plus post-hoc label
    switching correction.
